name: Crosswind! Air Canada 777-333ER [C-FITL] Bouncy Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Nothing like a good equipment swap! Here we have Air Canada's first 777 (delivered almost a decade ago now) making an interesting crosswind arrival on runway 17L this afternoon, subbing for a 767 flight that was cancelled earlier in the day. ATC is included, hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
